thread.title: Aircraft carrier sunk in WWII found in the Coral Sea

title: Aircraft carrier sunk in WWII found in the Coral Sea
text:
Aircraft carrier sunk in WWII found in the Coral Sea 2:21am GMT - 01:19 
An expedition crew has made a historic discovery in the Coral Sea: a U.S. aircraft carrier sunk after a four-day battle against Japanese forces in World War II. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
